Please provide the necessary information in five steps for an optimal quotation proposal tailored to your transportation needs.
Our vision is to help especially small and medium sized companies by offering comprehensive transport services that will help our business partners save costs, time and nerves.

Our specialization is air and ground transportation, and our services are adapted to these modes of transportation. If you order an import service, we will arrange the entire transport for you through our network of proven local expert partners who are members of the WCA (the largest global alliance of independent carriers) or JcTrans forwarders alliances. We handle export shipments from our Prague office through direct contact with airlines or their local representatives. We can offer transportation in following modes:
Land transport goes hand in hand with air transport. We can offer both a dedicated vehicle for time-sensitive shipments, as well as cost-optimal loading that saves costs and the environment.
We carry out ground transportation exclusively through verified partners with sufficient insurance coverage.
At WE-DEL we are certified dangerous goods experts certified by the International Aviation Association IATA.
We will be happy to arrange for you preparation of shipment according to the IATA Dangerous goods regulation and then transport it via air to your desired location.
Give us the time frame by which you need your shipment to arrive and leave the worries to us.

Is the linestopper hanging in the air at the car factory? Do you have an excellent business opportunity where timing to market is the key? Then there is a priority air/ground cargo service for you, especially suitable if you are very concerned about the delivery time. We see a story in every shipment, even on a non-financial level. We believe that the shipping business is about personal relationships and failure to meet deadlines can have unfathomable financial and non-financial consequences.
SMART air service offers the optimal ratio between transit time and price for imports from China.

Guarantee! If, for any reason within WE-DEL's control, the transit time is not met, you will be invoiced for the price of the Budget service instead of the price of the Smart service.
Give us your budget for transportation, we will try to find a solution through ground or air partial loading.

Budget is an economic service where the lowest possible price is a priority, in the case of air transport, the transit time is within 14 days from dispatch. In the case of land transport, we will try to find capacity nearby, thereby saving costs and the environment in order to maximize the utilization of the given means of transport.
We will be very happy if you turn to us with confidence with your request for transport services.

Tailored Solution for Your Freight Success

We don't want a world full of corporations where we become just passive recipients of the decision which international corporation to choose despite all of them has the same services wrapped in a different marketing package. Big corporations are usually doing services for another big corporations and small and medium enterprises are not getting service with the same quality and price. With this vision, we decided to found WE-DEL. Small and medium-sized enterprises are the healthy backbone of our economy, yet their share of GDP in the Czech Republic is below the level of the EU28. To a certain extent, this is also due to the fact that the mentioned enterprises encounter barriers from the large players from various sectors in the market. We want to change that!
Our vision is to help especially small and medium-sized companies by offering comprehensive transport services that will help our business partners save costs, time and nerves.
The satisfaction of our customers is at the core of our efforts.
We possess the ability to swiftly adapt to change, recognizing its constant presence.
We consistently strive to innovate our processes to deliver an exceptional customer experience.
Feedback and cooperation are the driving forces behind our service.
We consistently explore new approaches to service in order to foster our growth.
We proactively assume initiative and complete responsibility for our shipments.

What is your prefered mean of communication?

At first there are three means of communication online chat, email and call. For order/quote related communication e-mail is essential, while phone call is the fastest mean of communication. In case you dislike anything, do not hesitate to give us a call so we can find a address your feedback. As foretold feedback is mother of partnership and mutually beneficient cooperation.
Can I ship all around the world with WE-DEL?

Well, almost yes! Of course there are some exceptions. We cant offer shipment to: Cuba, North Korea, Iran, Syria, Belarus, Sudan, South Sudan, Yemen, Somalia, Burma (Maymar) and of course to Russia. At WE-DEL we believe that the firm spine is more important then profit. Additional check-ups may apply to the shipment that raise a suspicion that might be transfered to Russia through various transit countries.
Which shipments is WE-DEL able to transfer?

WE-DEL is able to transfer everything via Air/ground transport. Our service is mostly designed for time-critical shipments and cost-effective shipments above 70 kg. But no worries we can also provide you transport or smaller parcels via our courier partners for competitive prices.

At WE-DEL ve value your time a lot. Therefore you can approach as anytime via phone call. At our regular work hours, which is from Monday to Friday 08-17 CET we will try our utmost best tol reply you within one hour from sending of mail infromation. For OnTime service you can give us a call 24/7/365.
Is my shipment insured against any damage/losage of cargo?

As a freight forwarding company the cargo you are shipping with us is governed by insurance of our carrier. With that said it is by Montreal & Warszaw agreement in the case of air transport and by CMR in case of ground transport. On top of it WE-DEL has insurance with limit 3 000 000 CZK for freight-forwarding related mistakes. If your shipment exceeds this amouth, do not hesitate to write us for additional insurance.
How can I track my shipment?

We are having tracking option on the page. If for any reason the tracking is not giving updated informations we are always awailable to check the shipment progress via phone/mail/online chat. As for our premium service OnTime we are offering 24/7 tracking.

We understand the importance of your request and are committed to providing you with a prompt response. However, if your request requires immediate attention and cannot wait for a response via email, we kindly request that you reach out to us directly via phone call. Our dedicated contact number is +420 727 893 073.
